OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,FA deputy head teacher at Ysgol Dyffryn
OL,7,FAman wrote to the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fthree months before the stabbing of
OL,9,Ftwo teachers and a pupil, to express
OL,10,Fconcerns about pupils' behaviour.
OL,12,FCeri Myers took on the role of Deputy
OL,13,FHeadteacher at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman in
OL,14,FSeptember 2023. He told S4C's current
OL,15,Faffairs programme Y Byd ar Bedwar that
OL,16,Ftargeted attacks on staff were
OL,17,Fincreasing.
