OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,FHe said, "I got punched in the back of
OL,7,Fthe head. That was deemed as a once in
OL,8,Fa career incident. I've probably had
OL,9,Ffive or six once-in-a-career incidents
OL,10,Fwhich I've dealt with this last year
OL,11,F(2023/2024) academic year."
OL,13,F"There's a number of occasions where
OL,14,Fweapons have been brought into the
OL,15,Fschool, including a knife."
