OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,FIn January 2024, Ceri wrote to the
OL,7,FWelsh Government to express concerns
OL,8,Fabout vapes, pupil behaviour and what
OL,9,Fhe describes as a lack of clarity in
OL,10,Fgovernment guidelines for addressing
OL,11,Fit. Ceri was particularly concerned
OL,12,Fabout the difference between the
OL,13,Fpowers in Wales and England to search
OL,14,Fpupils for prohibited items.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
