OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F467A1739918724
OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"There were a series of emails where
OL,7,Fthe Government came back and palmed me
OL,8,Foff to some extent. I said I wasn't
OL,9,Fhappy with their response and I wanted
OL,10,Fa further conversation. The last email
OL,11,Fwas sent on the morning of the attack
OL,12,Fin Ysgol Dyffryn Aman."
OL,14,FCeri and the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fexchanged seven emails between January
OL,16,F2024 and the morning of the attack on
OL,17,F24 April 2024. Two teachers, Fiona
OL,18,FElias and Liz Hopkin, along with a
OL,19,Fstudent, were injured in the stabbing.
