OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"You never go into a school thinking
OL,7,Fthat would happen, but I believe that
OL,8,Fthere were warning signs for every
OL,9,Fschool in Wales that something like
OL,10,Fthis was going to happen."
OL,12,FA Freedom of Information request to
OL,13,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman revealed that
OL,14,Fduring the 2023/2024 academic year,
OL,15,Fthere were four recorded incidents of
OL,16,Fweapons being brought onto school
OL,17,Fpremises, yet only two pupils were
OL,18,Fpermanently excluded.
