OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"We're coming at the problem from two
OL,7,Fdifferent perspectives. The local
OL,8,Fauthority doesn't support the
OL,9,Fdecisions we need to make."
OL,11,FIn a joint statement, the Leader of
OL,12,FCarmarthenshire County Council, Cllr
OL,13,FDarren Price, and the Headteacher of
OL,14,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman, Mr. James
OL,15,FDurbridge, said: "Carmarthenshire
OL,16,FCounty Council and Ysgol Dyffryn Aman
OL,17,Fare very proud of the excellent
OL,18,Frelationship that exists between the
OL,19,FLocal Authority and the School.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]
