OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"Following the conclusion of the
OL,7,Frecent trial, the County Council has
OL,8,Freferred the case, in relation to the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of the incident of 24
OL,10,FApril 2024, to the Regional
OL,11,FSafeguarding Board and we are awaiting
OL,12,Ftheir decision as to the format and
OL,13,Ftimeline of the multi-agency review.
OL,15,F"We are not aware of incidents where
OL,16,Fthe School and Local Authority have
OL,17,Fbeen working against each other or in
OL,18,Fdisagreement with one another. We will
OL,19,Frespond to any of the findings the
OL,20,Findependent multi-agency review may
OL,21,Fidentify."
