OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,FAfter the incident at Ysgol Dyffryn
OL,7,FAman, Ceri Myers resigned from his
OL,8,Fposition as Deputy Headteacher and is
OL,9,Fnow working at an academy in London,
OL,10,Fwhere he oversees pupil safety and
OL,11,Fbehaviour. The Welsh Government has
OL,12,Fmet with Ceri to discuss his concerns.
OL,13,FHowever, he has since returned to work
OL,14,Fat the academy, continuing to lead on
OL,15,Fpupil safety and behaviour.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/15
