OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"We're developing a behaviour toolkit
OL,7,Ffor schools to help schools to manage
OL,8,Fchallenging behaviour and we also have
OL,9,Fstrong guidance in place on what can
OL,10,Fbe reasons for exclusion and
OL,11,Fcurrently, having a knife in school
OL,12,Fcan be a reason for automatic
OL,13,Fexclusion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/15
