OL,3,CWelsh Government 'palmed off' concerns
OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"We absolutely haven't been sleeping
OL,7,Fat the wheel and I've seen
OL,8,Fcorrespondence from the gentleman that
OL,9,Freferred to teachers being able to
OL,10,Fsearch for vapes and drugs and they
OL,11,Fcan already undertake those searches
OL,12,Fwith consent but as I've said our
OL,13,Fguidance is very clear on the issue of
OL,14,Fknives. They can be a cause for
OL,15,Fimmediate exclusion. In relation to
OL,16,Fwhat happened at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman,
OL,17,Fobviously my heart goes out to
OL,18,Feverybody at the school."
