OL,4,Cat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman before attack
OL,6,F"Now that the trial is over we need to
OL,7,Flook at everything that happened in
OL,8,Fthe run up to that day to understand
OL,9,Fwhat happened and learn any lessons.
OL,10,FIn our behaviour summit we are going
OL,11,Fto be bringing together local
OL,12,Fauthorities, practitioners and trade
OL,13,Funions to look at some of these
OL,14,Fissues."
OL,16,FFor the full story watch Y Byd ar
OL,17,FBedwar on Monday, 17 February, at 8pm
OL,18,Fon S4C, S4C Clic and BBC iPlayer with
OL,19,FEnglish subtitles.
